  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;The Accountability Initiative works to improve service delivery in India by developing innovative models for tracking government programs, disseminating this information to policymakers and citizens, and researching how to strengthen accountability between citizens and their government. This grant will allow the Initiative to track government funding by state rather than by sector. It also will deepen the work to understand how teachers and district staff can better monitor schools and respond to citizen demands.&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
